OL,3,CFamily appeal for information as
OL,4,Cmystery surrounds death of man found
OL,5,Cin pond
OL,7,FThe family of a 21 year-old found dead
OL,8,Fin a pond near Merthyr Tydfil two
OL,9,Fmonths ago, are pleading for help to
OL,10,Ffind out the circumstances surrounding
OL,11,Fhis death.
OL,13,FThe body of Bradly Hawkins, a father
OL,14,Fof two, was found in the water at the
OL,15,FPenywern Pond in Dowlais at 1.30pm on
OL,16,Fthe 24th February by a passer-by.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
