OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776974758
OL,3,CFamily appeal for information as
OL,4,Cmystery surrounds death of man found
OL,5,Cin pond
OL,7,FBradly's car was found at the side of
OL,8,Fthe lake with the doors left open and
OL,9,Fthe headlights still on. However, the
OL,10,Fkeys were no longer in the ignition
OL,11,Fand only Bradly's passport was left
OL,12,Finside.
OL,14,FHis family say most of Bradly's
OL,15,Fpossessions had disappeared.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776974758
OL,3,CFamily appeal for information as
OL,4,Cmystery surrounds death of man found
OL,5,Cin pond
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police say they're still
OL,8,Ftreating his death as "unexplained",
OL,9,Fbut Bradly's family say they have been
OL,10,Ftold by the coroner that he did not
OL,11,Fdie of drowning, and there were no
OL,12,Fsigns of trauma or injury.
OL,14,F"Bradly was actually missing a
OL,15,Fnecklace, a watch. He always went
OL,16,Feverywhere with his watch and his
OL,17,Fnecklace on," says Bradly's uncle Luke
OL,18,FBouchard.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776974758
OL,3,CFamily appeal for information as
OL,4,Cmystery surrounds death of man found
OL,5,Cin pond
OL,7,F"He had no money on him. The car keys
OL,8,Ffor the car were missing, the car
OL,9,Fdoors were open. The car had been
OL,10,Fransacked."
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police says they are not
OL,13,Fcurrently treating Bradly's death as
OL,14,Fsuspicious but they are seeking
OL,15,Ffurther information.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
