OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776974758
OL,3,CFamily appeal for information as
OL,4,Cmystery surrounds death of man found
OL,5,Cin pond
OL,7,FBradly was last seen on CCTV pictures
OL,8,Fpicking up a takeaway at 10.30pm on
OL,9,Fthe 23rd February. Police officers
OL,10,Fthen attempted to stop Bradley's car
OL,11,Fat 00:48 am on the 24th February.
OL,13,FThey are now appealing for any CCTV or
OL,14,Fdashcam footage between 00:45 and
OL,15,F01:15 on that date of Bradly's dark
OL,16,Fgrey Audi A3 sport, with a
OL,17,Fregistration plate of FR12 LSU, being
OL,18,Fdriven around the following locations
OL,19,Fin Merthyr Tydfil:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776974758
OL,3,CFamily appeal for information as
OL,4,Cmystery surrounds death of man found
OL,5,Cin pond
OL,7,FPolice say that if anybody has any
OL,8,Finformation they can contact them, and
OL,9,Fquote reference 2600059134.
OL,11,FBradly's family say they do not
OL,12,Fbelieve that he was alive when his car
OL,13,Farrived at the Penywern Pond, but that
OL,14,Fhis body had entered the water. His
OL,15,Fphone was later found discarded in
OL,16,Fbushes nearby, with his vape alongside.
OL,18,FBradley's family say they want answers
OL,19,Fto how their relative died.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776974758
OL,3,CFamily appeal for information as
OL,4,Cmystery surrounds death of man found
OL,5,Cin pond
OL,7,F"We just want to know what happened to
OL,8,FBradly," said his uncle Luke Bouchard.
OL,10,F"This is not about blaming someone, or
OL,11,Ftrying to get some sort of revenge for
OL,12,Fwhat happened. We just want to know
OL,13,Fwhat happened to Bradly."
OL,15,FLuke and the rest of Bradly's family
OL,16,Fare going often to lay flowers at a
OL,17,Fmemorial created alongside the lake
OL,18,Fwhere his body was pulled out.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
